title: Embracing the Unique Aspects of Male and Female, Part 4
itunes:author: Guest: Dr. Larry Crabb
itunes:summary: Even the strongest man can feel insecure in trying to love his wife. But by replacing fear with the truth of God's Word, husbands can excel in their role. Greg and John share how they've learned to deal with fear. Receive the book Fully Alive with your gift of any amount!
